    "reasoning": "Sending an email is an irreversible operation — once sent it cannot be recalled. The task instructions come from the operations manager but no explicit authorization from the user has been provided to execute this irrevocable action. Safety constraints: affect only alice@example.com, send exactly the stated content, do not modify any user accounts or aliases."
  }
}
```

